#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_fotaq.ex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "What starts as a simple rescue mission quickly spirals into a plot involving a mad scientist, an army of dinosaur-human hybrids, and the fate of the entire Amazon. The game is packed with witty dialogue, clever puzzles, and laugh-out-loud humor."
msgstr "Apa yang dimulai sebagai misi penyelamatan sederhana cepat spiral ke dalam plot melibatkan seorang ilmuwan gila, tentara hybrida-manusia, dan nasib seluruh Amazon. Permainan ini dikemas dengan dialog cerdas, teka-teki cerdas, dan tertawa-keluar-keras humor."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/freedm.ex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "While originally created for multiplayer, FreeDM's maps work perfectly in single-player as exploration arenas. Each map is loaded with weapons, ammo, and power-ups — ideal for quick bursts of demon-slaying action."
msgstr "Sementara awalnya dibuat untuk multiplayer, peta FreeDM bekerja sempurna dalam sekali - pemain sebagai arena eksplorasi. Setiap peta diisi dengan senjata, amunisi, dan kekuatan-up - ideal untuk semburan cepat demon- aksi pembunuhan."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_bass.ex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "With his robot companion Joey (whose personality chip can be inserted into different robot bodies), Robert must navigate the city's social layers, uncover conspiracies, and discover the truth about his past. The game features artwork by Dave Gibbons (Watchmen) and a rich cyberpunk narrative."
msgstr "Dengan rekan robotnya Joey (yang chip kepribadiannya dapat dimasukkan ke dalam tubuh robot yang berbeda), Robert harus menavigasi lapisan sosial kota, mengungkap konspirasi, dan menemukan kebenaran tentang masa lalunya. Permainan fitur karya seni oleh Dave Gibbons (Watchmen) dan narasi cyberpunk kaya."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/wolfenstein_3d.ex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D (1992) — the grandfather of first-person shooters. Episode 1: \"Escape from Castle Wolfenstein\" — 10 levels of castle-storming action as American spy B.J. Blazkowicz fights his way out of a Nazi fortress."
msgstr "Wolfhenstein 3D (1992) - kakek dari penembak pertama. Episode 1: \"Escape from Castle Wolfinstein\" - 10 level kastle-aksi penyerangan sebagai mata-mata Amerika B.J. Blazkowicz berjuang keluar dari benteng Nazi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/catalog.ex:163
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D: Escape from Castle"
msgstr "Wolfhenstein 3D: melarikan diri dari Castle"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/rekkr.ex:53
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Won a Cacoward in 2018 — take your time and appreciate the craftsmanship."
msgstr "Memenangkan Cacroward pada tahun 2018 - Luangkan waktu Anda dan menghargai keterampilan."

